</del></div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content"><note place="marginleft"><ab facs="#facs_548_r1l1">der brıef ward </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_548_r1l2">ʒum Neẅnmarkt </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_548_r1l3">geſchıkt bey <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>m</expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_548_r1l4">botten Do wolt </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_548_r1l5">Jn nyemants </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_548_r1l6">nemen als der </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_548_r1l7">hercʒog <expan>Jm<ex>m</ex></expan> lant </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_548_r1l8">niht was . alſo </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_548_r1l9">ward der brıef </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_548_r1l10">herwıder bracht </ab></note>
<ab facs="#facs_548_r2l19"><expan>Gnedıg<ex>er</ex></expan> <expan>h<ex>er</ex>re</expan> als vns eẅr <expan>hoch<ex>wirdikeit</ex></expan> <expan>verſchr<ex>iben</ex></expan> hat von vıſchkarren vnd </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_548_r2l20">pferds <expan>weg<ex>en</ex></expan> daʒ ein dem <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>n</expan> <expan>genome<ex>n</ex></expan> ıſt <expan>word<ex>en</ex></expan> etc das <expan>habe<ex>n</ex></expan> wır wol </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_548_r2l21"><expan>vernom<ex>en</ex></expan> vnd <expan>laſſ<ex>en</ex></expan> eẅr <expan>fürſtenl<ex>ich</ex></expan> gnade <expan>wıſſ<ex>en</ex></expan> daʒ Hanns <expan>ʒüllvıſch<ex>er</ex></expan> <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex></expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_548_r2l22"><expan>b<ex>urger</ex></expan> vor <expan>etlıche<ex>n</ex></expan> <expan>ʒeıt<ex>en</ex></expan> für vns kam Vnd klagt vns vvıe . der wölfel vogt ʒu </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_548_r2l23">Henffenuelt v̈lein vnd <expan>pet<ex>er</ex></expan> <expan>H<ex>e</ex>r</expan> hartungs <expan>vom<ex>m</ex></expan> <expan>Eglofſt<ex>ein</ex></expan> knecht Jm ſein </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_548_r2l24">pferd vıſch vnd karren / auf des Reıchs <expan>ſtraſſ<ex>en</ex></expan> <expan>genome<ex>n</ex></expan> <expan>hette<ex>n</ex></expan> on recht </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_548_r2l25">daran ſıe vns vnd den <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>n</expan> gar vnrecht getan <expan>habe<ex>n</ex></expan> / als eẅr gnade </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_548_r2l26">auch wol <expan>v<ex>er</ex>ſteeen</expan> mag / Als denn eẅr <expan>hoch<ex>wirdikeit</ex></expan> meldt von <expan>ſelıg<ex>er</ex></expan> gedechtnuſſ </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_548_r2l27">keyſer vnd <expan>and<ex>er</ex>r</expan> <expan>fürſt<ex>en</ex></expan> vnd <expan>h<ex>er</ex>ren</expan> brıef vnd gebott <expan>weg<ex>en</ex></expan> etc . <expan>Bıtte<ex>n</ex></expan> wir </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_548_r2l28">eẅr <expan>fürſtenl<ex>ich</ex></expan> gnade ʒu <expan>wıſſ<ex>en</ex></expan> / daʒ wır von <expan>löblıch<ex>er</ex></expan> gedechtnuſſ <expan>Römiſch<ex>en</ex></expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_548_r2l29"><expan>keyſ<ex>er</ex>n</expan> vnd <expan>künıg<ex>en</ex></expan> / auch <expan>gnedıkl<ex>ich</ex></expan> gefreyt vnd begnadt ſeın . Neͣmlıch </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_548_r2l30">was man von ſpeıs vnd von trank . ʒu vnd von <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>r</expan> ſtat füret </ab>
<pb facs="#facs_549" id="273v"/>
<ab facs="#facs_549_r1l1">treıbt <expan>od<ex>er</ex></expan> tregt . wıe es <expan>daru<ex>m</ex>b</expan> beſteen ſol . VVıe <expan>daru<ex>m</ex>b</expan> wellen die </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_549_r1l2"><expan>vorg<ex>enante</ex>n</expan> drey / dem <expan>eg<ex>enanten</ex></expan> <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>m</expan> <expan>b<ex>urger</ex></expan> / ſein hab <expan>wıd<ex>er</ex>keren</expan> vnd vnklaghaft </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_549_r1l3"><expan>daru<ex>m</ex>b</expan> machen . ſo das beſchıht ſo wellen wır den <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>n</expan> <expan>eẅr<ex>er</ex></expan> <expan>hoch<ex>wirdikeit</ex></expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_549_r1l4">ʒu eren . weıſen das von Jn ʒu <expan>neme<ex>n</ex></expan> Vnd vns vmb <expan>eẅr<ex>er</ex></expan> <expan>gnad<ex>en</ex></expan> <expan>wılle<ex>n</ex></expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_549_r1l5"><expan>günſtıkl<ex>ich</ex></expan> <expan>geg<ex>en</ex></expan> Jn darinn <expan>beweıſ<ex>en</ex></expan> / Denn wo wır <expan>eẅ<ex>r</ex>n</expan> <expan>fürſtenl<ex>ich</ex></expan> <expan>gnad<ex>en</ex></expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_549_line_1592204725884_2758">dıenſt vnd wolgefallen etc <expan>dat<ex>um</ex></expan> ut <expan>ſ<ex>upra</ex></expan> </ab>
</div>
<div type="cedula"><ab facs="#facs_549_line_1592204778657_2789">Cettula </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_549_line_1592204784813_2794"><expan>Gnedıg<ex>er</ex></expan> <expan>h<ex>er</ex>re</expan> der knecht der vns <expan>eẅr<ex>er</ex></expan> <expan>gnad<ex>en</ex></expan> brıef von der ſache <expan>weg<ex>en</ex></expan> <expan>geantw<ex>ur</ex>t</expan> hat der </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_549_line_1592204791199_2799">hat kein <expan>antw<ex>ur</ex>t</expan> <expan>daru<ex>m</ex>b</expan> an vns <expan>erford<ex>er</ex>t</expan> noch ſuſt <expan>nyema<ex>n</ex>ts</expan> / alſo <expan>ſchık<ex>en</ex></expan> wır <expan>eẅ<ex>r</ex>n</expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_549_line_1592204830428_2827"><expan>gnad<ex>en</ex></expan> <expan>dıeſ<ex>elb</ex></expan> <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex></expan> antwurt bey <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex></expan> ſelbs <expan>bott<ex>en</ex></expan> </ab>
</div>
</div><div type="regularised"><pb facs="#facs_548" id="273r"/><!--The following div is the container for the adress lines of the letter.-->
